Text: Forwarding Infofound out today what my email and direct number will be out in LA Regards David

RE MBA CandidateForwarded by David MartinHOUECT on PM Margaret Dutton on PM To David Martin cc Subject RE MBA Candidate Many thanks for your strong referral David Glad to have you continuing your alum referrals this year I have added your note to Mr Rogers application file and his file will receive priority handling once it reaches the MBA Admissions office Margaret Dutton Graduate School of Business MBA Admissions The University of Texas at Austin Original Message From David Martin mailto Sent Friday February PM To Subject MBA Candidate Margaret My name David Martin I graduated from the MBAMPA program at UT in May and I am currently a Manager at Enron North America in the Restructuring Group I am writing to you in reference to a Fall MBA candidate named Benjamin Rogers He is an Associate here at Enron and in my opinion an excellent candidate for the UT MBA program He has already submitted his application and is anxiously awaiting a response Ben came to Enron as an Analyst and was recently promoted to an Associate something not many Analysts are able to do He has worked in several groups throughout Enron and is very serious about the possibility of attending UT Please take my highest of recommendations into consideration when you assess his entrance into the program Thank you Regards David Martin
